Generic multi-database configuration.

Create migrations:
    alembic revision --autogenerate -m "cambios"

Make migrations in SQlite:    
    alembic upgrade head --x batch=true

Make migrations for MariaDB & PostgreSQL:
    alembic upgrade head


Conectar con PostgreSQL :SQLALCHEMY_DATABASE_URL = "postgresql://user:password@ip_servidor:5432/nombredb"

Conectar con MariaDB: SQLALCHEMY_DATABASE_URL = "mysql+pymysql://user:password@ip_servidor:3306/nombredb"

Conectar desde alembic: sqlalchemy.url = postgresql://user:password@ip_servidor:5432/nombredb
